release_note: Spanish language support has been added.
Minor wording corrections were made. Updated advertisements.
Chinese Simplified is now supported. Fixed a bug that the value was not displayed correctly when changing the passcode lock time.
Improved performance and stability. Fixes related to advertisements.
Specification changes were made regarding passcodes.
The settings screens and cells have been modified.
AirPrint is now supported. You can print out the contents of notes from the action button on the note edit screen for individual notes or from Share All Notes on the settings screen for all notes.
Fixed a bug that prevented app icon from being displayed on the iPad. Fixed a bug that cells were not highlighted when tapping cells in the note list screen.

Changed the timing of when authentication is required to when the app enters the foreground instead of when the app is activated to keep the app consistent. Fixed several minor bugs. Internal structure has been modified. The display method of items on the settings screen has been partially corrected.

The tap area at the top of the screen when switching between showing and hiding tools in the note list screen has been expanded horizontally. When the tool is hidden you can also switch to show it by tapping the bottom of the screen. Also when the app is restarted it will always start with the tools displayed. Reviewed error handling in the program. Minor corrections were made.
Added a search function for notes.
Some UI fixes have been made for the iOS15 release. Basic functions have been improved.
Added the ability to use Face ID or Touch ID to unlock apps.
Added the ability to display an indicator during iCloud sync. Fixed a bug related to iCloud.
When iCloud is not available the status is now displayed in the settings screen. Minor fixes.
Fixed some of the issues related to iCloud syncing.
Added iCloud feature. Now you can sync iCloud with other devices and backup your notes data to iCloud.
Changed the UI of the date control to popup. Basic functions have been improved.
Fixed a bug that the date is not displayed when editing the date.
Added the ability to share all entries. Few bug fixes.
